entry.string: The same registered ID (#(1)) was found belonging to a #(2) module in the file system and a registered #(3) module in the database. Please correct this and regenerate the list.
entry.translation: Zee seme-a regeestered ID (#(1)) ves fuoond belungeeng tu a #(2) mudoole-a in zee feele-a system und a regeestered #(3) mudoole-a in zee detebese-a. Pleese-a currect thees und regenerete-a zee leest. Um de hur de hur de hur.

entry.string: The module #(1) is found with two different registered IDs, #(2) in the file system and #(3) in the database. Please correct this and regenerate the list.
entry.translation: Zee mudoole-a #(1) is fuoond veet tvu deefffferent regeestered IDs, #(2) in zee feele-a system und #(3) in zee detebese-a. Pleese-a currect thees und regenerete-a zee leest. Um de hur de hur de hur.
